\s UPawuli uvusa uYutikusi ekufeni
\p
\v 7 Kwathi ngo\add suku\add* lokuqala lweviki\x + 1 Kor. 16.2. Isam. 1.10.\x*, abafundi bebuthene\x + 20.7,30.11.26.\x* ukuhlephula isinkwa\x + 20.11. 2.42,46. 1 Kor. 10.16. 11.20-24.\x*, uPawuli watshumayela kubo, elungele ukusuka kusisa, waseselula ilizwi kwaze kwaba phakathi kobusuku.
\v 8 Njalo kwakukhona izibane ezinengi\x + Mat. 25.1. Joha. 18.3. Isam. 4.5. 8.10.\x* endlini ephezulu ababebuthene kiyo\x + 1.13.\x*.
\v 9 Kwakuhlezi ewindini ijaha elithile ngebizo linguYutikusi, elajunywa yibuthongo obukhulu\x + 2 Kor. 11.33.\x*, uPawuli esetshumayele isikhathi eside, selehlulwe yibuthongo lawela phansi lisuka esitezi sesithathu\x + 1 Kho. 17.19.\x*, laselidojwa lifile.
\v 10 Kodwa uPawuli wehla waziphosela phezu kwalo\x + 1 Kho. 17.21. 2 Kho. 4.34.\x*, e\add li\add*singatha wathi: Lingakhathazeki; ngoba umphefumulo walo ukhona kilo\x + Mat. 9.24.\x*.
\v 11 Esenyukile njalo esehlephule isinkwa wadla\x + 20.7.\x*, wakhuluma labo isikhathi eside kwaze kwasa, ngokunjalo wahamba.
\v 12 Basebemletha umfana ephila, basebeduduzwa hatshi lakancane.
\s UPawuli eMilethu; uvalelisa abeEfesu
\p
\v 13 Kodwa thina, sesihambe phambili ukuya emkhunjini, sasuka ngomkhumbi saya eAsosi, lapho siqonde ukumkhweza uPawuli; ngoba wayemisile ngokunjalo, yena ebezahamba ngenyawo.
\v 14 Njalo esehlangene lathi eAsosi, samkhweza safika eMithilene,
\v 15 sasuka lapho ngomkhumbi, kusisa safika maqondana leKiyosi; langomhlomunye sasondela eSamosi; sasesihlala eTrogiliumu, ngolulandelayo\x + Luka 13.33. Seb. 21.26.\x* safika eMilethu\x + 20.17. 2 Tim. 4.20.\x*.
\v 16 Ngoba uPawuli wayezimisele ukuyiceza iEfesu ngomkhumbi\x + 18.19.\x*, ukuze angalibali eAsiya; ngoba wayephanga, nxa kwakungenzeka kuye, ukuba seJerusalema\x + 18.21. 19.21. 24.17.\x* ngosuku \w lwePentekoste\w**\x + 2.1. 1 Kor. 16.8. Seb. 20.6. Levi 23.6,11,15.\x*.
